Weather was overcast. Sun was dull but could see it. Wind was calm. Temperature in the 80's. Loon seen swimming.
Weather was clear. Temperature in the 80's. Wind was breezy.
Weather was bright clear day. Sunny. Wind was breezy from NW. Cool day temperature in high 60's. Saw a number of sunfish swimming on the way out. Heard geese in the distance but did not see.
Weather overcast. off and on rain.Temperature in 70's. Pair of loons on lake.
Sunny and windy. Wind from the South. Temperature in 80's. Spotted many sunfish near shore on way in.
Sunny and breezy. Temp. around 80. Loons on the lake. Sun fish near shore. Grandkids were along to help.
Busy boating day on the lake. Clear skies. Great boating recreation day in a vacation week.
Calm day. Little boating observed. Pair of loons on lake. Partly cloudy.
